  <brief_title>NSAIDs in Coronary Artery Disease Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-steroidal Anti-inflammatory Drugs Impair the Platelet Inhibiting Effect of Acetylsalicylic Acid in Coronary Artery Disease Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
